category: Devel
requires: cygwin libboost1.53 libgcc1 libstdc++6 tcl
sdesc: "Programmable verification and analysis tool for C++"
ldesc: "Vera++ is a programmable tool for verification, analysis and
transformation of C++ source code. Vera++ is mainly an engine that parses C++
source files and presents the result of this parsing to scripts in the form of
various collections - the scripts are actually performing the requested tasks."
